00:44:27,745 --> 00:44:30,648
We've slept in! We've slept in!

500
00:44:30,722 --> 00:44:33,144
We've gotta be on the tracks
in 30 minutes.

501
00:44:34,819 --> 00:44:36,608
Where in the bloody hell's Malky?

502
00:44:39,012 --> 00:44:39,994
(BANGING ON DOOR)

503
00:44:40,068 --> 00:44:42,719
GRAEME: Malky! Malky!

504
00:44:46,021 --> 00:44:47,777
We're late.

505
00:44:51,430 --> 00:44:54,213
MALKY: I've rebuilt Old Faithful for you.

506
00:44:56,679 --> 00:44:58,501
She's ready if you're ready.

507
00:44:58,567 --> 00:45:00,356
Malky, you wee beauty.

508
00:45:34,351 --> 00:45:36,839
That clock should be set.
What's wrong with it?

509
00:45:36,911 --> 00:45:40,523
- ANNE: I think he slept in as well.
