974
01:30:57,141 --> 01:30:58,571
You're level.

975
01:31:00,118 --> 01:31:01,580
Come on.

976
01:31:03,286 --> 01:31:05,458
<i>One or two turns of the wheel
will be the difference</i>

977
01:31:05,527 --> 01:31:07,600
<i>between these two great athletes.</i>

978
01:31:21,019 --> 01:31:24,882
<i>The Flying Scotsman has won
the World Championship for the second...</i>

979
01:31:27,355 --> 01:31:29,658
<i>This is surely his greatest achievement!</i>

980
01:31:29,820 --> 01:31:33,017
<i>One of the most exciting races
I have ever seen.</i>

981
01:31:33,085 --> 01:31:34,427
Yes!

982
01:31:35,774 --> 01:31:37,268
Yes, mate!

983
01:31:37,342 --> 01:31:41,882
<i>Obree is once again World Champion.
